ActivityInfo (40 bytes): </b>The <b>Fixed_Portion</b> of a <b>FAX_SERVER_ACTIVITY</b>
(section <a href="86c61ea7-73a5-4e3d-a8f2-a293667ebb12" data-linktype="relative-path">2.2.19</a>)
structure that contains information about the server activity that has changed.
This event SHOULD only be sent when the messages counters in the server
activity structure change. No event is sent when an event log entry is added on
the server.</p>
